WEBVTT

00:00:07.725 --> 00:00:11.711
ظآزI found a faint light
in the fading duskظآز

00:00:11.712 --> 00:00:15.311
ظآزAnd met your steady gazeظآز

00:00:15.312 --> 00:00:24.132
ظآزOne knowing glance,
and side by side we walk onظآز

00:00:24.575 --> 00:00:27.061
ظآزLonging finds no place to restظآز

00:00:27.062 --> 00:00:29.211
ظآزThrough drifting wind and rainظآز

00:00:29.212 --> 00:00:32.699
ظآزYou are the prayer within my handsظآز

00:00:32.700 --> 00:00:40.324
ظآزA single second frozen,
tears in focus, my heart already knowsظآز

00:00:40.325 --> 00:00:42.786
ظآزWe made a promise long agoظآز

00:00:42.787 --> 00:00:44.786
ظآزFor all our days to comeظآز

00:00:44.787 --> 00:00:48.449
ظآزYou are the fate I cannot outrunظآز

00:00:48.450 --> 00:00:53.836
ظآزHow much must I let go
to trade for one moment?ظآز

00:00:53.837 --> 00:00:56.457
ظآزHolding you closeظآز

00:00:56.637 --> 00:00:58.874
ظآزWould that be enough?ظآز

00:00:58.875 --> 00:00:59.619
=Echoes of Love=

00:00:59.620 --> 00:01:01.499
(Adapted from the signed screenplay
Echoes of Love on Migu Reading)

00:01:01.500 --> 00:01:03.732
=Episode 11=

00:01:10.740 --> 00:01:13.099
Come take a look.

00:01:16.139 --> 00:01:18.819
Where have you been these past few days?

00:01:19.059 --> 00:01:20.260
Are you all right?

00:01:21.020 --> 00:01:23.900
Thank you for your concern. I am well.

00:01:44.100 --> 00:01:45.980
Have a look around.

00:01:48.540 --> 00:01:49.700
Take a look.

00:01:50.580 --> 00:01:51.698
Official Gu,

00:01:51.699 --> 00:01:53.379
it is your birthday today.

00:01:53.380 --> 00:01:54.338
How about

00:01:54.339 --> 00:01:56.220
we go set off a sky lantern together?

00:02:09.460 --> 00:02:10.620
Official Gu,

00:02:10.939 --> 00:02:12.220
happy birthday.

00:02:12.580 --> 00:02:14.220
May you be safe year after year.

00:02:17.262 --> 00:02:23.400
ظآزStrangers meet again,
the past ablaze in vivid huesظآز

00:02:24.360 --> 00:02:27.559
ظآزA sharp arrow pierces through memoryظآز

00:02:27.560 --> 00:02:31.319
ظآزLonging spreads like inkظآز

00:02:31.320 --> 00:02:38.040
ظآزBeaded curtains divide love
and hate at either endظآز

00:02:38.280 --> 00:02:45.120
ظآزAfter endless sorrow enduredظآز

00:02:45.480 --> 00:02:48.179
ظآزPast ties fade like a dream gone coldظآز

00:02:48.180 --> 00:02:49.300
Miss Song,

00:02:50.059 --> 00:02:51.099
that day...

00:02:56.260 --> 00:02:57.460
What happened?

00:03:07.059 --> 00:03:08.379
Gu Chengye,

00:03:08.860 --> 00:03:09.874
you were right.

00:03:09.875 --> 00:03:11.218
I overreached.

00:03:11.219 --> 00:03:12.895
Shanguan Yu is no decent person.

00:03:13.980 --> 00:03:16.220
She only saw me as a source of money.

00:03:16.275 --> 00:03:18.395
By day they forced me to dress up,

00:03:19.139 --> 00:03:21.139
and at night they locked me
in the punishment room.

00:03:23.939 --> 00:03:25.780
I even doubted you before.

00:03:27.980 --> 00:03:29.979
I truly did not know any better.

00:03:38.539 --> 00:03:39.859
I am sorry.

00:03:50.020 --> 00:03:51.139
Song Zhiyun,

00:03:51.939 --> 00:03:53.620
who told you to come here?

00:03:57.059 --> 00:03:58.699
Shanguan Yu.

00:03:58.939 --> 00:04:00.099
Gu Chengye.

00:04:01.059 --> 00:04:03.060
Surely you know

00:04:03.539 --> 00:04:05.379
what kind of place Huanyue House is.

00:04:06.140 --> 00:04:07.379
Shanguan Yu,

00:04:07.740 --> 00:04:09.859
is this how Huanyue House
conducts itself?

00:04:10.212 --> 00:04:12.086
I recall warning Zhou Zihua

00:04:12.087 --> 00:04:13.859
that Song Zhiyun is under my protection.

00:04:16.580 --> 00:04:18.659
Are you courting death?

00:04:25.979 --> 00:04:27.739
Shanguan Yu, remember this.

00:04:28.060 --> 00:04:30.978
You, Zhou Zihua, and Huanyue House,

00:04:30.979 --> 00:04:34.140
Sooner or later,
I will make you all pay.

00:04:36.937 --> 00:04:39.020
The next time we meet,

00:04:39.500 --> 00:04:41.260
it will not be your hair I take.

00:05:03.339 --> 00:05:05.099
Gu Chengye is suspicious by nature.

00:05:05.637 --> 00:05:06.918
Do it.

00:05:07.525 --> 00:05:09.124
I can endure anything.

00:05:28.979 --> 00:05:30.340
(Gu Chengye,)

00:05:30.820 --> 00:05:32.419
(now)

00:05:33.140 --> 00:05:35.059
(I will be the one
who wields the blade.)

00:05:53.462 --> 00:05:55.422
Keep this with you.

00:05:57.900 --> 00:05:58.811
This is...

00:05:58.812 --> 00:06:00.778
This is the imperial
Tianshan Snow Lotus Balm.

00:06:00.779 --> 00:06:01.978
Apply it externally

00:06:01.979 --> 00:06:03.178
twice a day.

00:06:03.179 --> 00:06:04.220
Within days,

00:06:04.979 --> 00:06:06.499
the wounds on your back will heal.

00:06:07.460 --> 00:06:08.659
Thank you.

00:06:13.339 --> 00:06:15.098
Be sure to apply it on time.

00:06:15.099 --> 00:06:17.419
I have official duties to attend to.

00:06:18.060 --> 00:06:19.419
I will not be at the residence.

00:06:21.179 --> 00:06:22.380
Take care of yourself.

00:06:23.060 --> 00:06:25.099
I will.

00:06:40.339 --> 00:06:43.260
(It seems he has
completely lowered his guard.)

00:06:43.580 --> 00:06:45.520
(I must find the Beauty Portrait
as soon as possible.)

00:06:48.020 --> 00:06:48.579
Wei Cheng.

00:06:48.580 --> 00:06:49.019
Yes.

00:06:49.020 --> 00:06:50.699
- Prepare the carriage.
- Yes, Official. Where to?

00:06:50.700 --> 00:06:52.299
Seal Huanyue House.

00:06:53.099 --> 00:06:54.659
- On what grounds?
- Any will do.

00:06:57.539 --> 00:06:59.019
By order of the Imperial Guard,

00:06:59.020 --> 00:07:01.539
Huanyue House is to
be sealed effective immediately.

00:07:02.500 --> 00:07:04.978
Official Gu certainly
carries great authority.

00:07:04.979 --> 00:07:06.978
May I ask how we humble townsfolk,

00:07:06.979 --> 00:07:08.978
honest merchants making a living,

00:07:08.979 --> 00:07:11.299
have offended you?

00:07:11.659 --> 00:07:14.419
And on what grounds

00:07:14.739 --> 00:07:16.979
do you seal Huanyue House?

00:07:18.339 --> 00:07:20.059
Fire hazards,

00:07:20.339 --> 00:07:22.059
illicit liquor,

00:07:22.112 --> 00:07:23.872
harboring prostitutes.

00:07:24.460 --> 00:07:25.379
In short,

00:07:25.380 --> 00:07:28.019
the Imperial Guard
has a thousand reasons

00:07:28.020 --> 00:07:29.220
to shut you down.

00:07:29.339 --> 00:07:30.900
Very well, Official Gu.

00:07:31.859 --> 00:07:33.299
Just

00:07:33.659 --> 00:07:35.580
seal it if you wish.

00:07:37.460 --> 00:07:40.499
But Huanyue House
will reopen soon enough.

00:07:41.260 --> 00:07:44.619
Do you know
who stands behind Huanyue House?

00:07:45.339 --> 00:07:46.659
Heaven itself.

00:07:48.700 --> 00:07:50.739
Can you defy Heaven?

00:07:51.140 --> 00:07:52.260
Heaven?

00:07:58.060 --> 00:08:00.140
You mean the Shengtang Guild?

00:08:05.539 --> 00:08:07.460
The Beauty Portrait is in my hands.

00:08:08.825 --> 00:08:11.307
I intend to overturn your Heaven.

00:08:16.539 --> 00:08:17.900
Official Gu,

00:08:19.339 --> 00:08:21.900
it is only an erotic painting.

00:08:22.299 --> 00:08:23.659
Can you truly win a case with that?

00:08:26.500 --> 00:08:28.659
Do you know who the

00:08:29.380 --> 00:08:30.419
real beasts are?

00:08:38.579 --> 00:08:39.580
Seal it.

00:08:39.662 --> 00:08:41.461
Whoever dares unseal it without orders

00:08:41.462 --> 00:08:43.859
will be invited to
the Imperial Guard for questioning.

00:09:12.380 --> 00:09:14.499
(Something this important)

00:09:14.500 --> 00:09:16.170
(must be hidden in his room.)

00:09:18.179 --> 00:09:19.779
(I wonder whether inside)

00:09:19.980 --> 00:09:22.207
(there are any records
about Gu Chengye's mother.)

00:09:36.900 --> 00:09:38.682
(The Gu Family Chronicle)

00:09:39.980 --> 00:09:41.698
(The fifth year of Shaoyuan,)

00:09:41.699 --> 00:09:44.418
(Gu Yunde followed the Founding Emperor
in campaigns north and south,)

00:09:44.419 --> 00:09:45.739
(rendering distinguished service.)

00:09:45.740 --> 00:09:47.339
(He was granted the title of Duke)

00:09:47.340 --> 00:09:48.778
(and married Lady Meng.)

00:09:48.779 --> 00:09:50.259
(The sixth year of Shaoyuan,)

00:09:50.260 --> 00:09:51.778
(his beloved son, Chengye, was born,)

00:09:51.779 --> 00:09:53.698
(adding an heir to the Gu family.)

00:09:53.699 --> 00:09:54.960
(The fourteenth year of Shaoyuan,)

00:09:54.960 --> 00:09:56.979
(the Battle of the Wastelands
was won in great victory,)

00:09:56.980 --> 00:09:58.519
(bringing further honor
to the Gu family.)

00:09:58.519 --> 00:10:01.000
(Lady Meng was suddenly stricken with
a strange illness and hanged herself.)

00:10:01.162 --> 00:10:02.962
(Official Gu has returned.)

00:10:16.740 --> 00:10:18.499
Official Gu has returned.

00:10:18.500 --> 00:10:19.298
Song Zhiyun,

00:10:19.299 --> 00:10:21.220
do not tell me you are here

00:10:21.900 --> 00:10:23.578
to warm my bed.

00:10:23.579 --> 00:10:24.700
I...

00:10:27.699 --> 00:10:29.499
Actually

00:10:29.779 --> 00:10:32.259
I am afraid of thunder, so...

00:10:34.340 --> 00:10:35.300
Why are you still here?

00:10:38.779 --> 00:10:39.899
Fine, I will go.

00:10:44.779 --> 00:10:45.739
Wait.

00:10:52.600 --> 00:10:54.180
(The Gu Family Chronicle)

00:10:56.500 --> 00:10:58.259
What else do you require, Official Gu?

00:11:20.779 --> 00:11:22.499
You did not apply the medicine on time.

00:11:23.340 --> 00:11:24.259
Very well.

00:11:24.717 --> 00:11:25.970
I will apply it for you.